               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18350511-name-402" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18350511-name-402" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18350511-name-402" type="surname" value="POLLARD"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18350511-name-402" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM POLLARD</persName>
                  </hi>. I am the prisoner's father, and am a basket-maker, and work in Fleet-lane—I have four children—the prisoner lived at home with me. On the 21st of April he boarded and lodged with me—my daughter and wife missed this property on the morning of the 22nd, and on the 23rd, at night, when he came home, I gave him in charge for stealing it.</p>
