                  </hi>. I live at Mr. Clarges, a pawnbroker, in Aldersgate-street. I have a gown and shawl pawned on the 21st of April for 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.—I cannot swear to the prisoner—I have seen him at our shop.</p>
